---
import Layout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - AI Colleagues">
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8">Last updated: February 16, 2026</p>

        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          <p>
            AI Colleagues respects your privacy. This page describes what information we collect,
            why we collect it, and how you can request access or deletion.
          </p>

          <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Contact details submitted through our contact form.</li>
            <li>Basic website usage data (for reliability and analytics).</li>
            <li>Operational logs required to secure and improve our services.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Respond to project inquiries and support requests.</li>
            <li>Operate and improve website reliability and performance.</li>
            <li>Maintain security, abuse prevention, and legal compliance.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell personal information. We only share data with trusted service providers
            needed to operate the website and communications.
          </p>

          <h2>Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We keep personal data only as long as needed for business operations, legal requirements,
            and security purposes.
          </p>

          <h2>Your Rights</h2>
          <p>
            You can request access, correction, or deletion of your personal information by contacting
            us at <a href="mailto:privacy@ai-colleagues.com">privacy@ai-colleagues.com</a>.
          </p>

          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For privacy-related questions, email
            {' '}<a href="mailto:privacy@ai-colleagues.com">privacy@ai-colleagues.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
